To build this branch you require the latest version of pax-exam. Therefore do the following steps:

git clone git://github.com/ops4j/org.ops4j.pax.scanner.git
cd org.ops4j.pax.scanner
mvn clean install
cd ..

git clone git://github.com/ops4j/org.ops4j.pax.runner.git
cd org.ops4j.pax.scanner
mvn clean install
cd ..

git clone git@github.com:ops4j/org.ops4j.pax.exam1.git
cd org.ops4j.pax.exam1
mvn clean install

